## Nullability and Undefined

- Use optional chaining (`?.`) for potentially undefined properties
- Use nullish coalescing (`??`) instead of logical OR (`||`) for undefined values
- Add null checks for potentially undefined values:
  ```typescript
  if (results.metrics?.complexity) {
    // safe to use
  }
  ```